    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/35b51e3f46bc288ceb500203ffdec532.avif?t=1762756099\" width=600 height=125 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a relentless quest to reclaim the wilds. Dinosaurs Dominion is built around <strong>action based combat</strong>, <strong>story driven exploration</strong>, and <strong>layered progression</strong>. Inspired by roguelite design, each journey is self-contained where progress is earned through both exploration and conquest, while lasting impacts carry over between runs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/37482c3be9e358b4d843e62b0272f4ef.avif?t=1762756099\" width=616 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/0b6768a761d1b1902e0fd74bd9e910e0.poster.avif?t=1762756099\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/0b6768a761d1b1902e0fd74bd9e910e0.webm?t=1762756099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/0b6768a761d1b1902e0fd74bd9e910e0.mp4?t=1762756099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off in personal, <strong>high-stakes</strong>, <strong>one on one combat</strong>, a test of timing, spacing, and skill. Every fight rewards patience, punishes recklessness, and demands vigilance as you wait for your moment to strike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/e13322d9440079dd9a0f6c4f1467706e.avif?t=1762756099\" width=616 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/2e389ccb90c9f91d4c750c7386325a32.poster.avif?t=1762756099\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/2e389ccb90c9f91d4c750c7386325a32.webm?t=1762756099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/2e389ccb90c9f91d4c750c7386325a32.mp4?t=1762756099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roam freely across <strong>diverse biomes</strong>. From lush forests to ashen wastes and snow covered cliffs. Uncover secrets, discover ancient landmarks, and unlock new species along the way. Each region tells its own story, and every step brings you closer to reclaiming the wild.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/6ef85795ca4f6008c2c7cd8f4a94e9c6.avif?t=1762756099\" width=616 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/cadee757bbe83994fd5e13283010fee0.poster.avif?t=1762756099\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/cadee757bbe83994fd5e13283010fee0.webm?t=1762756099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/cadee757bbe83994fd5e13283010fee0.mp4?t=1762756099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock mutations</strong> that suit your playstyle and sharpen your instincts with each victory, while defeat returns you to the start.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/506cf160148ac709a5576a6b2ad9cf05.avif?t=1762756099\" width=616 height=36 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>14 playable dinosaurs</strong>, from nimble scouts to towering juggernauts, each with a playstyle defined by size, power, and mobility.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>13 mutations</strong> that let you evolve, specialize, and experiment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3 open-world maps</strong>, each with unique biomes and environmental storytelling.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Focused <strong>one on one combat</strong> inspired by Souls-like design.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Roguelite progression</strong> with single-run challenges and permanent impact across journeys.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Landmarks</strong>, Relics, and Echoes that reward exploration with meaningful discoveries.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Totems and Trophies</strong>, unlockable rewards that reveal deeper insights into the world.</p></li></ul>",
